<paragraph blockId="55.[151,1436,152,658]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">
In general, the page numbers for the species named and described by Kuhl are often cited incorrectly. In part because Kuhl’s “Die Deutschen Fledermäuse” was published for the first time in 
<quantity box="[1169,1258,552,578]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.61518" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" unit="in" value="1817.0">1817 in</quantity>
Hanau (pp. 1– 67), while in 1818 the same work was reprinted in the 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Annalen der Wetterauischen Gesellschaft für die gesamte Naturkunde</emphasis>
, Frankfurt am Main in two parts (pp. 11–49; pp. 185–215).
</paragraph>
